title: ﻿क्या उत्तर प्रदेश पुलिस ने सुरक्षा कर्मियों को ‘नमो’ फ़ूड पैकेट्स बाँटकर बीजेपी का प्रचार किया?
author: www.factcrescendo.com
vclaim: BR Tiwari, Addl. Chief Election Officer on reports of Namo food packets being distributed in Noida: We came to know about this from media reports.
